question: how high is the share of people living in proximity of a busstop in zürich?
sql:
select iv.value from indicator_values2 iv
join indicators i on iv.indicator_id = i.indicator_id
join spatialunit s on iv.spatialunit_id = s.spatialunit_id
where i.name like 'Access by bus [% of inhabitants]' and s.name like 'Zürich'

question: how many municipalities have a share of people living in proximity of a busstop higher than 44 per year?
sql:
select iv.year, count(*) from
indicator_values2 iv
join indicators i on iv.indicator_id = i.indicator_id
join spatialunit s on iv.spatialunit_id = s.spatialunit_id
where iv.VALUE > 44 and s.type_id = 1 and i.name like 'Access by bus [% of inhabitants]' group by iv.year

select min(iv.value), s.name from indicator_values2 iv
join indicators i on iv.indicator_id = i.indicator_id
join spatialunit s on iv.spatialunit_id = s.spatialunit_id
where s.type_id=4 and iv.year=2013 and i.name like 'MIV share (modal split) [%]'
